  "body": "In order to wrap up and finish up a testnet release:\r\n\r\n- [x] Recommend --clear-db for testnet users to prevent unresolvable error conditions on restarts\r\n- [x] On querying chain head, poll forever until the first response is received, then begin a timeout to receive more chain head responses\r\n- [x] RPC service for querying validator activation\r\n- [x] Minor changes to our website, giving users more options to obtain faucet funds or other ways of installing Prysm by linking to the Gitbook docs\r\n- [x] Break ties in fork-choice",
